1. Write an application using TCP connection, define the class Client that has library as type String, lender name of type string and arraylist of books borrowed of type integer.
Define the function void sendtoserver (String library, String lender, Arraylist borrowedbooks) which sends to server. (5 marks)
Define the class Server that has insertintoDB to store the library, lender name, array list of books borrowed so far.

Note: Any Database can be used to store the information. 
      Client should be more than one
      
